FW Portland Real time address listpst Original Message From Platter Phillip Sent Tuesday March PM To Bishop Serena Gang Lisa Subject Portland Real time address list Serena Lisa I have not been getting the EPE preschedules I think there is more than one address group out there for real time The correct group is as follows DLUBSWEnergyRealPortlandRealTime Thanks ALot

FW EES CA SCHEDULE for pst Original Message From Frazier Michael Sent Monday March PM To Bishop Serena EES Power Settlements Jackson Jeffrey Subject EES CA SCHEDULE for Importance High The attached schedule is for Wednesday March and includes the impact of discontinued scheduling for IBM Please be advised that this schedule could be revised early tomorrow morning before AM or in time to post to the ISO based on further discussion with PGE concerning the IBM accounts Please call if you need further information Text files compatible with this forecast have already been posted to Sparky Michael R Frazier Manager Load Forecasting Enron Energy Services Office Pager Pmail

FWpst Original Message From Rawson Lester Sent Friday February PM To Bishop Serena Subject RE Serena Heres the El Paso stuff OATI login SteveBuraczyk PW Sburac The scheduling contacts are PSCO Nadine is the contact for the PV sales Dan does the Eddy County scheduling EPE can be reached at Tony Steve You already have the procedure and swap information Call me if there are quesitons If any Valley Electric questions come Paul Choi is the expert Les Original Message From Bishop Serena Sent Friday February AM To Rawson Lester Subject Les I have a meeting for about then I will be back can we go over the EL Paso stuff then I have to leave again at about Sorry for the change of plans regards Serena

PREPAYSPST Chris a couple things about the prepays for Is the Avista possible additional powera done deal or is it a day to day basis When should it be scheduled Could you email the details on your prepay deals to Phil and I just in case we have questions regarding them I have looked over the calculation sheet you showed me yesterday Tuesday for the wire to Avista and I have found a mistake We are not currently delivering to City of Shasta Lake mw RTC Serena

California schedulingPST Due to the tentative completion date of the UBS deal I think it would be wise for me to resume the duties of scheduling the California book as of Monday February After meeting with Murray I am under the impression that as of Wednesday you will be on UBS time and will not be doing the scheduling for the estate Let me know if you see a flaw in this plan thanks Serena Bishop

Monday CA ImportsPST Hey Guys Please check congestion for all imports coming into California for Flow Date Monday on Sunday during the interim market about AM STSW is especially concerned with the PV import To check CONG see the OASIS Web Site transmission tab DA Interim Branch Group Congestion Usage Charges If there is congestion during the interim market in excess of please call me Thanks Serena

Hood to Coast RelayPST Hood To Coast Relay Enron North America will be sponsoring a Hood to Coast Relay Team for next years competition Aug The event starting at Timberline and ending in Seaside is a great challenge and a lot of fun The team will be composed of Enron employees so if you are interested in participating in North Americas most popular relay spending a day and a half with your fabulous unshowered coworkers eating bagels and bananas and running on little if any sleep or have a simply brilliant idea for a team name please reply no later that October th For more details on the event visit wwwhoodtocoastcom Run On Serena Bishop

RE New Logins needed Old logins need to be deletedPST Cara I still cant get into Oati am I doing something wrongI am using the ID and password you have below Thanks Serena Original Message From Semperger Cara Sent Friday February AM To Cc Purcell Mike Bishop Serena Subject New Logins needed Old logins need to be deleted Importance High Good Morning I need new logins created for the following people SerenaBishop pw welcome MikePurcell pw welcomeback I need the following logins deleted Lisa Gang Susie Wilson Stacy Runswick Within a couple of weeks most of the Enron folks will no longer be active and I will have no access to the system Mike Purcell will be handling the account and can be reached at Please call me at within the hour if there is additional information that you need to set up Serena and Mikes logins by the end of today Thanks Cara Semperger West Power Scheduling Supervisor Enron North America

TAG PST Hey Guys Well I had to learn some Cod Scheduling fast this afternoon we really do need to exchange new cell phone numbers Anyway tag was incorrect and BPA called about I cancelled that tag and replaced it with tag I hope what I did was okay let me know if I should have done it differently On the NW sheet that tag number is highlighted in yellow in case there is a problem I assume the something needs to be corrected in the preschedule workspace but I dont know what it is so I will leave it to Cara or Donald to explain it to me in the morning Thanks again Serena
